Steven Lofchie, a partner at 
Cadwalader, Wickersham & Taft LLP, Jean-Paul Musicco, a partner 
at Trail Angel Finance LLC, John Egan, director of global prime 
finance at Deutsche Bank AG and Will Duff Gordon, a senior 
researcher at Data Explorers, participate in a panel discussion 
about hedge funds and short selling.  They speak at Bloomberg World Headquarters in New York. 
Bloomberg's Adam Johnson moderates the discussion. (Source: 
